    "name": "Rogue Rhythm",
    "steam_appid": 3091990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/e516eb7c149afa76cf34ce2553b295b8.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/e516eb7c149afa76cf34ce2553b295b8.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight  60 different minions and 10 different bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Discover 1-8 variants of each minion and log them in your Journal</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy your enemy with both 5-key and 2-key rhythm-game mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each boss introduces a new mechanic </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize your loadout by playing against your enemy's weaknesses (or with your strengths)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get a performance score at the end of the battle and compare it to your best</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with the <i>DEMON</i> or <i>OMNIPOTENT</i> difficulty settings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/df0a4665af0b80452a1b7fdf9e221a1b.apng?t=1740270144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/df0a4665af0b80452a1b7fdf9e221a1b.poster.avif?t=1740270144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/d68094350d352717d57384ba7d577f07.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/d68094350d352717d57384ba7d577f07.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/d6ebe6263b60943cc56a91837b3d64f9.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/d6ebe6263b60943cc56a91837b3d64f9.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel between 30 procedurally generating dungeon floors </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each set of 3 floors changes the theme from Cave, Nature, Ocean, etc.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the procedural algorithm in order to reach the end in as few moves and battles as possible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/360569816ba7e867eda92cd6e1463d4c.apng?t=1740270144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/360569816ba7e867eda92cd6e1463d4c.poster.avif?t=1740270144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=120 height=120 /></picture></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/d68094350d352717d57384ba7d577f07.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/d68094350d352717d57384ba7d577f07.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/71404d35d04d0ebe42f4bae87d4fcb5e.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/71404d35d04d0ebe42f4bae87d4fcb5e.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect 204 different items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even early-game sets are viable because all sets provide similar power but different effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each boss drops a unique item or grants an effect that will change how you play the game  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure you aren't missing anything by checking your Collection Log</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/b25e17d1d70e8ef41cb36540d7cb6093.apng?t=1740270144\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/b25e17d1d70e8ef41cb36540d7cb6093.poster.avif?t=1740270144\" class=\"bb_img\" width=160 height=160 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/d68094350d352717d57384ba7d577f07.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/d68094350d352717d57384ba7d577f07.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras/892149da4cb6783bdd032d35e850273f.avif?t=1740270144\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091990/extras_big/892149da4cb6783bdd032d35e850273f.avif?t=1740270144 width=800 height=119 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to 41 different beats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And 10 different ambient tracks </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sound effects and design by Hubert &quot;Maeror&quot; Łabuda</p></li></ul>",
